    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The ability to interpret and critically evaluate visible objects, actions, or symbols encountered in the environment, especially in works of art, television, and films.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
